玩家启动游戏后进入[[程序化生成|程序生成]]的小岛<ref>{{Cite web | last = Plunkett | first = Luke | date = 2019-03-12 | title = Islanders Looks Like The Cutest Lil' City-Building Game | publisher = G/O Media | url = https://kotaku.com/islanders-looks-like-the-cutest-lil-city-building-game-1833246254 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210113040542/https://kotaku.com/islanders-looks-like-the-cutest-lil-city-building-game-1833246254 | archive-date = 2021-01-13 | access-date = 2021-01-15 | website = [[Kotaku|Kotaku]]}}</ref>，岛屿分多种风格，有些地形不能放置个别类型建筑<ref name="HCG" /><ref name="TGM" />。玩家开始前可从两种建筑包二选一，每种都有一定数量的建筑，包含林业、农业和渔业等类别<ref name="HCG" /><ref name="CriticalHit">{{Cite web | last = Barbosa | first = Alessandro | date = 2019-04-09 | title = Islanders review–Streamlined, simple and satisfying | url = https://www.criticalhit.net/review/islanders-review-streamlined-simple-and-satisfying/ | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200930153805/https://www.criticalhit.net/review/islanders-review-streamlined-simple-and-satisfying/ | archive-date = 2020-09-30 | access-date = 2021-01-15 | website = Critical Hit}}</ref>。从[[電子遊戲術語列表|仓库]]选中的建筑周围呈现半透明球体，显示新建筑与其他建筑或树木等自然物体所需隔开的距离，以及放在各处能拿到的分数<ref name="HCG">{{Cite web | last = Cunningham | first = James | date = 2019-04-08 | title = Review: Islanders | url = https://hardcoregamer.com/2019/04/08/review-islanders/328413/ | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2019-10-11 | access-date = 2021-01-15 | website = Hardcore Gamer | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191011111152/https://www.hardcoregamer.com/2019/04/08/review-islanders/328413/}}</ref><ref name="Edge">{{Cite magazine | date = 2019-07 | title = Play: ''Islanders'' | magazine = [[Edge_(杂志)|Edge]] | publisher = [[未來出版社|Future plc]] | pages = 120–121}}</ref><ref name="PCGamer" />。不同建筑选中后的半透明球体尺寸不一<ref name="TGM">{{Cite web | last = Paschetto | first = Nicoló | date = 2019-04-19 | title = Islanders – Recensione | url = https://www.thegamesmachine.it/islanders-pc/islanders-recensione-pc/ | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200605002744/https://www.thegamesmachine.it/islanders-pc/islanders-recensione-pc/ | archive-date = 2020-06-05 | access-date = 2021-01-15 | website = The Games Machine | publisher = Aktia srl}}</ref>。玩家确定建筑位置前就能看到所得分数，所以可以在岛上各处预览，自行决定最佳摆放地点<ref name=":2">{{Cite web | last = Donlan | first = Christian | date = 2019-04-18 | title = Islanders is a city-builder with new ideas | url = https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2019-04-18-islanders-is-a-city-builder-with-new-ideas | access-date = 2021-01-15 | website = [[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] | publisher = Gamer Network | archive-date = 2021-01-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210105005507/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2019-04-18-islanders-is-a-city-builder-with-new-ideas | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web | last = Hiller | first = Benja | date = 2019-04-17 | title = Islanders Review {{!}} Entspannter Städtebau {{!}} Ich will zurück nach Islanders | url = https://welcometolastweek.de/2019/04/17/islanders-review-entspannter-staedtebau-ich-will-zurueck-nach-islanders/ | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200919030056/https://welcometolastweek.de/2019/04/17/islanders-review-entspannter-staedtebau-ich-will-zurueck-nach-islanders/ | archive-date = 2020-09-19 | access-date = 2021-01-15 | website = Welcome To Last Week | publisher = 100kiloherz medien}}</ref>。建筑放在关联建筑旁边的得分更高，无关建筑放在一起分数偏低<ref name="Edge" />。以马戏团为例，靠近房屋分数较高，靠近大厦较少<ref name="PCGamer">{{Cite web | last = Livingston | first = Christopher | date = 2019-04-08 | title = Islanders is the most relaxing strategy game ever | url = https://www.pcgamer.com/islanders-is-the-most-relaxing-strategy-game-ever/ | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190526100558/https://www.pcgamer.com/islanders-is-the-most-relaxing-strategy-game-ever/ | archive-date = 2019-05-26 | access-date = 2021-01-15 | website = [[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] | publisher = Future plc}}</ref>。建筑方位一旦确定就不可更改，也不能铲除或在其上叠加，所以要想拿到高分，玩家必须谨慎选择<ref name="Edge" /><ref name="PCGamesN">{{Cite web | last = Pask | first = Kelly | date = 2019-04-10 | title = Islanders is the most relaxing city-builder I've ever played | url = https://www.pcgamesn.com/islanders/islanders-city-builder | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201124143006/https://www.pcgamesn.com/islanders/islanders-city-builder | archive-date = 2020-11-24 | access-date = 2021-01-15 | website = PCGamesN | publisher = Network N | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

建筑放到岛上后就从仓库消失，玩家分数达到预定值便能激活两个新建筑主题包并从中二选一，包裹内不但有已解锁建筑，还有刚刚选择的主题建筑<ref name="Edge" /><ref name=":1" />。如此循环往复，玩家得以解锁金矿、度假村等高级建筑，有些类别需满足更高标准才能放置，潜在得分也更多<ref name="HCG" /><ref name="RPS">{{Cite web | last = Meer | first = Alec | date = 2019-04-04 | title = Wot I Think: Islanders | url = https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2019/04/04/islanders-review/ | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201026153507/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2019/04/04/islanders-review/ | archive-date = 2020-10-26 | access-date = 2021-01-15 | website = [[Rock,_Paper,_Shotgun|Rock, Paper, Shotgun]] | publisher = Gamer Network}}</ref>。得分可填补屏幕底部进度条，全部充满后玩家就能点击前往下一个岛<ref name="HCG" />。解锁新建筑主题包或新岛后，下一次解锁所需分数上升<ref name="Polygon">{{Cite web | last = Marshall | first = Cass | date = 2019-04-05 | title = Islanders is a bite-sized palate cleanser of a civilization builder | url = https://www.polygon.com/reviews/2019/4/5/18296250/islanders-game-review | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190611165908/https://www.polygon.com/reviews/2019/4/5/18296250/islanders-game-review | archive-date = 2019-06-11 | access-date = 2021-01-15 | website = [[Polygon|Polygon]] | publisher = [[沃克斯传媒|Vox Media]]}}</ref>。玩家积满进度条后可以留在当前小岛继续游戏，自行决定是否前往下一个岛<ref name="Kotakureview">{{Cite web | last = Plunkett | first = Luke | date = 2019-04-04 | title = Islanders Is Almost The Perfect City-Building Game | url = https://kotaku.com/islanders-is-almost-the-perfect-city-building-game-1833729123 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190423220026/https://kotaku.com/islanders-is-almost-the-perfect-city-building-game-1833729123 | archive-date = 2019-04-23 | access-date = 2021-01-15 | website = Kotaku | publisher = G/O Media}}</ref><ref name="Verge">{{Cite web | last = Moore | first = Michael | date = 2019-04-28 | title = These two city-building puzzle games play very differently, but share a grim outlook on the environment | archive-date = 2019-08-02 | access-date = 2021-01-15 | website = [[The_Verge|The Verge]] | publisher = Vox Media | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190802124712/https://www.theverge.com/2019/4/28/18512527/islanders-20-minute-metropolis-simcity-nature-short-play | dead-url = no | url = https://www.theverge.com/2019/4/28/18512527/islanders-20-minute-metropolis-simcity-nature-short-play}}</ref>。如果玩家仓库中的建筑用完，或岛上没有位置摆放建筑，通往下一个岛屿的分数又不够，则游戏结束<ref name="CriticalHit" /><ref name="Edge" />。玩家分数是每轮游戏开始后在所有岛屿得分的总和，整体目标就是尽量提升得分<ref name="Nichegamer">{{Cite web | last = Streva | first = Frank | date = 2019-06-22 | title = Minimalist City Builder "Islanders" Gets Mac and Linux Support, Sandbox Mode | access-date = 2021-01-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190802124712/https://nichegamer.com/2019/06/22/minimalist-city-builder-islanders-gets-mac-and-linux-support-sandbox-mode/ | website = Niche Gamer | archive-date = 2019-08-02 | dead-url = no | url = https://nichegamer.com/2019/06/22/minimalist-city-builder-islanders-gets-mac-and-linux-support-sandbox-mode/}}</ref>。

游戏有意取消[[城市建造遊戲|城市建造遊戲]]的许多常见功能，如资源累积、流量管理和[[科技树|技术研究]]<ref name="TGM" /><ref name="PCGamer" /><ref name="RPS" />。游戏没有[[任务_(电子游戏)|支线任务]]或可选目标，只有简短的[[成就_(电子游戏)|成就]]清单供玩家达成<ref name="Edge" /><ref name="Millenium">{{Cite web | date = 2019-04-10 | title = Test: Islanders se fait une place sur nos PC. | url = https://fr.millenium.gg/news/329331.html | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2019-05-07 | access-date = 2021-01-15 | website = Millenium | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190507064321/https://www.millenium.org/news/329331.html | publisher = Webedia}}</ref>。《海岛文明》仅有的[[多人电子游戏|多人游戏]]元素是全球高分排行榜，列出玩家最高得分<ref name="RPS" /><ref name="Nichegamer" /><ref name="Millenium" />。

== 开发 ==
保罗·施耐普夫（{{lang|en|Paul Schnepf}}）、弗里德曼·阿曼罗德（{{lang|de|Friedemann Allmenröder}}）和乔纳斯·泰罗勒（{{lang|en|Jonas Tyroller}}）都在[[柏林工程与经济应用科学大学|柏林工程与经济应用科学大学]]（{{lang|en|HTW Berlin}}）研读[[电子游戏设计|电子游戏设计]]本科课程，三人共同组建灰熊游戏公司（{{lang|en|Grizzly Games}}）。施耐普夫和阿曼罗德大二时先行合作开发简短的实验游戏《{{lang|en|ROM}}》。<ref name="GWO-interview">{{Cite web | last = Nesterenko | first = Oleg | date = 2019-06-14 | title = Strategic minimalism behind indie hit Islanders | url = https://gameworldobserver.com/2019/06/14/islanders/ | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190823064230/https://gameworldobserver.com/2019/06/14/islanders/ | archive-date = 2019-08-23 | access-date = 2021-01-15 | website = Game World Observer | publisher = WN Media Group}}</ref>他们还在大二期间与同为学生的沙赫里亚尔·沙尔布（{{lang|en|Shahriar Shahrabi}}）合作，开发极简风格[[飛鼠裝滑翔運動|飛鼠裝滑翔運動]]模拟器《超级飞行》（{{lang|en|''Superflight''}}），并为发行创办灰熊游戏公司<ref name="GWO-interview" />。沙尔布在《超级飞行》发布后退出，泰罗勒大三时加入，《海岛文明》同年开始研发<ref name="Schnepf">{{Cite web | last = Schnepf | first = Paul | title = Islanders | url = https://paulschnepf.com/islanders | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210113065525/https://paulschnepf.com/islanders | archive-date = 2021-01-13 | access-date = 2021-01-13 | website = paulschnepf.com}}</ref>。

《海岛文明》开始开发后，首先是三周的研究、原型制作和构想完善。开发组成员儿时都很喜欢《[[纪元系列|纪元]]》、《[[工人物语系列|工人物语]]》和《[[模擬城市系列|模拟城市]]》等城市建造游戏，决定合作推动构想创作《海岛文明》。新游戏的[[软件开发过程|开发周期]]不长，共计七个月，其中四个月主开发期，另外三个月是发行前的完善和准备。<ref name="GWO-interview" /><ref name="Schnepf" />

阿曼罗德接受《游戏世界观察家》（{{lang|en|''Game World Observer''}}）采访时称，新作是将前作《超级飞行》探索的构想演变而成，特别是极简风格和程序化生成功能。游戏由三人共同制作，每人都需承担多道研发工序。三人决定将游戏设计尽量简化，每局游戏时间不至太长，以此减轻开发工作量，确保游戏机制不至太复杂的同时，又能足够好玩，有充足的[[重玩價值|重玩價值]]。<ref name="GWO-interview" />

游戏采用的程序化生成功能源自《超级飞行》开发。开发组编写脚本，用预生成模板迅速组建新关卡，以此检测游戏机制。三人发现，如果每次启动游戏都有新关卡，玩家就乐意反复探索，这样还不用延长开发时间，故而决定在《海岛文明》沿用。<ref name="GWO-interview" />阿曼罗德还称，开发游戏机制期间，团体反复讨论简化现有机制：“我们决定前都要扪心自问：能否再简单点儿？如果取消这种功能，游戏还好玩儿吗？”<ref name="GWO-interview" />游戏经过昼夜更替等众多版本更迭，最后采用以简化的距离评分机制<ref name="Schnepf" /><ref name="GWO-interview" />。

=== 发行与更新 ===
《海岛文明》采用[[Unity_(游戏引擎)|Unity 3D]]游戏引擎，2019年4月4日在[[Steam|Steam]]率先面向[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]平台发布<ref name="GWO-interview" /><ref name="Schnepf" />。灰熊游戏公司随后推出众多更新，为游戏增加新内容。早期更新加入新岛屿和建筑类别，如[[海藻养殖|海藻养殖场]]与纪念建筑；还有新游戏功能，如消除[[用户界面|用户界面]]内容以便全方位[[截圖|截圖]]的照片模式。<ref name="GWO-interview" /><ref>{{Cite web | last1 = Schnepf | first1 = Paul | last2 = Allmenröder | first2 = Friedemann | last3 = Jonas | first3 = Tyroller | date = 2019-05-07 | title = Islanders :: Content update I | dead-url = no | website = Steam | url = https://steamcommunity.com/games/1046030/announcements/detail/1626273522729385885 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190509050705/https://steamcommunity.com/games/1046030/announcements/detail/1626273522729385885/ | archive-date = 2019-05-09 | access-date = 2021-01-16 | publisher = Valve Corporation}}</ref>2019年6月，游戏推出最后一次重大更新，新增支持[[MacOS|macOS]]和[[Linux|Linux]]平台，另有不含积分机制的[[沙盒游戏|沙盒]]模式，玩家可以不受限制地选择建筑，还在正常游戏模式新增撤消按钮，可以去除上一次放置的建筑<ref name="Nichegamer" /><ref name="Techraptor-update">{{Cite web | last = Allen | first = Joseph | date = 2019-06-20 | title = Islanders Update Adds Sandbox Mode, Extended Support, And More | archive-date = 2020-11-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201108005556/https://techraptor.net/gaming/news/islanders-update-adds-sandbox-mode-extended-support-and-more | access-date = 2021-01-16 | website = TechRaptor | dead-url = no | url = https://techraptor.net/gaming/news/islanders-update-adds-sandbox-mode-extended-support-and-more}}</ref>。

