《海岛文明》获普遍好评，{{lang|en|[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]}}平均评分达82（最高100）<ref name="Metacritic">{{Cite web | title = Islanders | url = https://www.metacritic.com/game/pc/islanders | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200923062142/https://www.metacritic.com/game/pc/islanders | archive-date = 2020-09-23 | access-date = 2021-01-16 | website = Metacritic}}</ref>。评论称赞刻意简化的游戏机制，极简、朴素的视觉美感，以及轻松的音效设计<ref name="RPS" /><ref name="Polygon" /><ref name="Kotakureview" />。游戏商业表现也很亮眼，属2019年4月Steam最热销的20款新游戏<ref>{{Cite web | date = 2019-05-23 | title = Top Steam Releases of April 2019 | url = https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/593110/view/1630795514034259761 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210105005601/https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/593110/view/1630795514034259761 | archive-date = 2021-01-05 | access-date = 2021-01-16 | website = Steam Blog}}</ref>。2019年7月，《海岛文明》入选“[[Rock,_Paper,_Shotgun|Rock, Paper, Shotgun]]”网站年度最佳游戏<ref>{{Cite web | date = 2019-07-10 | title = The best games of 2019 so far | url = https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2019/07/10/the-best-games-of-2019-so-far/17/ | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190727071953/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2019/07/10/the-best-games-of-2019-so-far/17/ | archive-date = 2019-07-27 | access-date = 2021-01-16 | website = Rock, Paper, Shotgun | publisher = Gamer Network}}</ref>。卢克·普兰克特（{{lang|en|Luke Plunkett}}）在“[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]”网站发文，将本作列入2019年十佳游戏<ref>{{Cite web | last = Plunkett | first = Luke | date = 2019-12-17 | title = Luke Plunkett's Top 10 Games Of 2019 | url = https://kotaku.com/luke-plunketts-top-10-games-of-2019-1840470910 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191218202820/https://kotaku.com/luke-plunketts-top-10-games-of-2019-1840470910 | archive-date = 2019-12-18 | access-date = 2021-01-16 | website = Kotaku | publisher = G/O Media}}</ref>。该网站的保罗·塔马约（{{lang|en|Paul Tamayo}}）称赞《海岛文明》给予玩家非常轻松的享受<ref>{{Cite web | last = Tamayo | first = Paul | date = 2019-12-17 | title = 2019's Most Relaxing Games (And Most Stressful Ones) | url = https://kotaku.com/2019s-most-relaxing-games-and-most-stressful-ones-1840467620 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191219021945/https://kotaku.com/2019s-most-relaxing-games-and-most-stressful-ones-1840467620 | archive-date = 2019-12-19 | access-date = 2021-01-16 | website = Kotaku | publisher = G/O Media}}</ref>。

许多评论认可游戏的极简风格让人放松和思考<ref name="HCG" /><ref name="PCGamer" /><ref name="PCGamesN" /><ref name="Polygon" />。普兰克特认为《海岛文明》胜在纯粹，没有炫目夸张的旁枝末节转移玩家注意力，干扰游戏体验<ref name="Kotakureview" />。电子游戏杂志《[[Edge_(杂志)|Edge]]》和“{{lang|en|Rock, Paper, Shotgun}}”网站的亚历克·梅尔（{{lang|en|Alec Meer}}）都表示，摆放建筑的游戏机制令他们想到玩《[[俄羅斯方塊|俄羅斯方塊]]》时摆弄方块<ref name="Edge" /><ref name="RPS" />。评论员还称，操作简单促使玩家体验不同时长的玩法<ref name="TGM" />。许多评论对游戏只需很短时间就能玩上一盘赞不绝口<ref name="TIGW"/><ref name="Techraptor-review"/>。《Edge》杂志和“[[Polygon|Polygon]]”网站的卡斯·马歇尔（{{lang|en|Cass Marshall}}）声称，《海岛文明》就像“除味点心”，玩过更加复杂的游戏后，不如拿来放松一把<ref name="Edge" /><ref name="Polygon" />。还有评论认为，《海岛文明》本身就适合长时间玩<ref name="TGM" /><ref name="CriticalHit" /><ref name="Kotakureview" />。

部分文章关注游戏视觉风格。法国游戏网站“千禧年”（{{lang|en|Millenium}}）认为游戏整体颜色风格和物体形状与操作机制相辅相成<ref name="Millenium" />。“技术猛禽”（{{lang|en|TechRaptor}}）网站的塞缪尔·古列尔莫（{{lang|en|Samuel Guglielmo}}）自称喜欢以“好看”为标准摆放建筑，哪怕导致分数减少也在所不惜<ref name="Techraptor-review" />。《Edge》评论员与古列尔莫看法类似，“在效率和美之间苦苦挣扎”，同时赞扬“干净利落的几何（图像）风格”，即使专注拿高分而忽视美观，岛屿看上去还是很漂亮<ref name="Edge" />。德国独立杂志《欢迎来到上星期》（{{lang|en|''Welcome to Last Week''}}）刊登本杰·希勒（{{lang|en|Benja Hiller}}）的文章，声称很高兴游戏中没有人物：“没有讨厌的人类。没有谁会在你面前恶意地摆动手指说：‘路面损毁，多加小心’”<ref name=":1" />。

评论员认为《海岛文明》反映并鼓励哲学思维。“[[The_Verge|The Verge]]”网站的迈克尔·摩尔（{{lang|en|Michael Moore}}）认为，经过玩家操作，各个岛屿的原始自然环境逐渐由密集建筑取代，感觉就像“人类剥削自然”的真实再现<ref name="Verge" />。克里斯蒂安·唐兰（{{lang|en|Christian Donlan}}）通过“[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]”网站表达类似看法：“看着游戏中美丽而朴素的岛屿堆满建筑，这到底是值得兴奋的成就，还是危害自然的罪行？”他特别认可游戏设定不强求操作，玩家可以自行选择。<ref name=":2" />“独立游戏网站”（{{lang|en|The Indie Games Website}}）发表瑞安·杨（{{lang|en|Ryan Young}}）的评述，探讨《海岛文明》的“[[游戏态度|游戏态度]]”，即玩家乐于参与游戏并遵守各项规则的心态。在他看来，游戏节奏平缓，建筑摆放不理想又可能导致混乱，这些都会影响玩家的游戏态度<ref name=":0">{{Cite web | last = Young | first = Ryan | date = 2019-05-08 | title = Islanders Is A Dangerous Lesson In Entropy | url = https://www.indiegamewebsite.com/2019/05/08/islanders-is-a-dangerous-lesson-in-entropy/ | dead-url = no | website = The Indie Game Website | publisher = Game If You Are | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201223235953/https://www.indiegamewebsite.com/2019/05/08/islanders-is-a-dangerous-lesson-in-entropy/ | archive-date = 2020-12-23 | access-date = 2021-01-16}}</ref>。

部分评论批评游戏的极简设计理念。意大利游戏雜誌《游戏机器》（{{lang|en|The Games Machine}}）的尼科洛·帕斯切托（{{lang|it|Nicoló Paschetto}}）和“Rock, Paper, Shotgun”的爱丽丝·利古里（{{lang|en|Alice Liguori}}）都对游戏没有动画人物、岛屿缺乏生机感到失望<ref name="TGM" /><ref>{{Cite web | last = Liguori | first = Alice | date = 2019-07-09 | title = Have You Played… Islanders? | url = https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2019/07/09/have-you-played-islanders/ | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200923083303/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2019/07/09/have-you-played-islanders/ | archive-date = 2020-09-23 | access-date = 2021-01-16 | website = Rock, Paper, Shotgun | publisher = Gamer Network}}</ref>。还有评论批评游戏只有一首背景歌曲<ref name="Millenium" /><ref name="Techraptor-review" />。“千禧年”认为单纯积分的游戏机制太过单调，应该加入更多目标<ref name="Millenium" />。《Edge》杂志指出，建筑一旦摆放就无法更改，难免有些刻板；“暴击”（{{lang|en|Critical Hit}}）的亚历山德罗·巴博萨（{{lang|en|Alessandro Barbosa}}）也认为游戏没有撤消功能堪称败笔<ref name="CriticalHit" /><ref name="Edge" />。许多评论对[[Game_Over|game over]]后又要从早期的简洁岛屿重新开始深感郁闷<ref name="CriticalHit" />。瑞安·杨就称，从零开始感觉压力山大，他干脆不玩了<ref name=":0" />。拉胡尔·希尔克（{{lang|en|Rahul Shirke}}）在“{{lang|en|IND13}}”网站发文，希望新开局时增加岛屿尺寸和类型选择功能，减轻重新开始的挫折感；亚历克·梅尔建议加入玩家重置现有岛屿的功能<ref name="RPS" /><ref name="Ind13">{{Cite web | last = Shirke | first = Rahul | date = 2019-04-05 | title = Islanders – Review | url = https://www.ind13.com/islanders-review/ | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201224000007/https://www.ind13.com/islanders-review/ | archive-date = 2020-12-24 | access-date = 2021-01-16 | website = IND13}}</ref>。

